        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3851040058" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5125193163651848437">This was a beautiful autobiography that I only recently discovered. It is now a classic and is the parallel stories of the author growing up and his mother&apos;s childhood and raising of kids in Brooklyn and the Bronx. Full of love and life, it exposes the issues of racism through the life of this amazing Jewish woman who married an African American and raised 12 kids in poverty, none of whom became a junky or a loser. It is truly inspiring reading.</span>
  <span id="freeText5125193163651848437" style="display:none">This was a beautiful autobiography that I only recently discovered. It is now a classic and is the parallel stories of the author growing up and his mother's childhood and raising of kids in Brooklyn and the Bronx. Full of love and life, it exposes the issues of racism through the life of this amazing Jewish woman who married an African American and raised 12 kids in poverty, none of whom became a junky or a loser. It is truly inspiring reading.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5125193163651848437" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
